title: AudioCodes SBC call capacity
agents: snmp
catalog: applications/voip
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Monitors current inbound and outbound SBC calls, current sessions and the
 maximum values retained by the AudioCodes 15-minute KPI history.

 The Active Sessions values require SDR syslog or SDR local storage to be
 enabled on the AudioCodes device.

inventory:
 One service named {SBC Call Capacity} is created when the KPI objects exist.
